videos.description: Nick Weiler-Babb tosses an over-the-shoulder pass to George Conditt IV for a layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: Iowa State converts half-court pass into and-1 layup

videos.description: Cartier Diarra gets a steal off an Iowa State rebound and feeds Levi Stockard III in the paint for a layup, creating a trip to the foul line.
videos.headline: Kansas State's hustle leads to 2nd-chance points

videos.description: Lindell Wigginton dribbles around a screen and finds Marial Shayok cutting to the hoop for an easy layup.
videos.headline: Wigginton's slick pass leads to Shayok lay-in

videos.description: Tyrese Haliburton dumps it off to Lindell Wigginton, who drains a long 3-pointer to tie Kansas State in the second half.
videos.headline: Wigginton's deep 3-pointer ties it for Iowa State

videos.description: George Conditt IV cleans up Lindell Wigginton's miss with a powerful dunk to extend Iowa State's lead.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Conditt rises up for putback slam
